ESP32: TFT LCD Touchscreen Display – 2.8 inch ILI9341 240×320 (Arduino IDE) by Rui Santos

In this guide, you’ll learn how to get started with the TFT LCD Touchscreen Display with the ESP32 board. This TFT Touchscreen with 2.8 inch display (240×320 px) comes with the ILI9341 driver. This display is a great option to build graphical user interfaces (GUI) for your IoT projects.

Links:
- https://randomnerdtutorials.com/esp32-tft-touchscreen-display-2-8-ili9341-arduino/ (Complete project tutorial)
- https://randomnerdtutorials.com/esp32-pinout-reference-gpios/ (ESP32 Pinout Reference with explanations)
